          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Nuclear Worker Residual Contaminations Compensation Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Labor to oversee an independent study on residual nuclear contamination of workers at certain facilities owned or operated by contractors of the Department of Energy and subsidiaries of those contractors.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
